 And so your main chain will always stay

39:01.760 --> 39:04.480
 somewhat conservative and have the minimum viable amount

39:04.480 --> 39:06.320
 of expressiveness required on it

39:06.320 --> 39:08.880
 to do all kinds of interesting things.

