40:40.800 --> 40:43.400
 So the point of Plutus was let's create a language

40:43.400 --> 40:46.760
 where you can write these small to mid size programs

40:46.760 --> 40:48.280
 and have a high degree of confidence

40:48.280 --> 40:50.240
