 and said well how much they make and how much they pay

46:21.320 --> 46:22.760
 well imagine a tax system

46:22.760 --> 46:24.680
 where that's just done by default

46:24.680 --> 46:26.600
 or other social systems

46:26.600 --> 46:29.160
 where this type of information is put in by default.

