 and each of these pools will have different adherents

51:54.120 --> 51:56.520
 and actors and then you can actually balance out

51:56.520 --> 51:57.360
 the whole thing.

51:57.360 --> 51:59.920
 So as opposed to having one cult, you have many cults.

51:59.920 --> 52:00.760
 Exactly.

52:00.760 --> 52:01.600
 And they argue.

52:01.600 --> 52:02.440
 And the cults argue with each other

