2:19:05.800 --> 2:19:07.280
 Innovation stops.

2:19:07.280 --> 2:19:09.120
 The desire to actually do real work stops

2:19:09.120 --> 2:19:12.280
 because you're always inside this virtual economy.

2:19:12.280 --> 2:19:13.120
 So I don't know.

